title: Big Brother Canada After Dark S04E22 March 27, 2016
description: No episodes of After Dark have been missed! In case you did not see the updates that I posted on my wall here's what happened. No After Dark episodes have run since the fake evictions on Thursday. The only explanation given was "due to unforseen circumstances After Dark will return tomorrow". I have not bothered to check any deeper as to why but it appears to be back on track. I will always try to keep you up to date by posting on my wall on KAT
